com.i2group.apollo.auditservice

Interface IAuditService


  • public interface IAuditService
    A method for retrieving AuditEntrys about items in the Analysis Repository.

    Note: Unlike some other services in the Intelligence Analysis Platform, IAuditService is not affected by the presence of ProhibitedOperation indicators in the schema.

    Since:
    2.0

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      AuditResults retrieveAuditEntries(Calendar fromDate, Calendar toDate)
      Retrieves AuditResults containing AuditEntrys with timestamps between the specified dates.

    • Method Detail

      • retrieveAuditEntries

        AuditResults retrieveAuditEntries(Calendar fromDate,
                                Calendar toDate)
                                  throws InvalidArgumentException
        Retrieves AuditResults containing AuditEntrys with timestamps between the specified dates.
        Parameters:
        fromDate - A Calendar specifying the date the range should start from.
        toDate - A Calendar specifying the date the range should run to.
        Returns:
        See above.
        Throws:
        InvalidArgumentException - If either of the arguments is not valid.
